  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Demonstrators enter the alarm hall",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Demonstrators who were involved in the people's uprising that is taking place today demanding the resignation of the President and the Prime Minister entered the President's House and started a demonstration while they were besieging the President's House during the day.",
        "In this case, it is to be noted that the protestors who have entered the Prime Minister's official residence Alari Malikai complex are also protesting there."
      ],
